{
  "stem": "1249.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But one day in Auschwitz, they said, we need 500 girls.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So they counting people and-- in one room, or one-- I don't know, it was barrack or whatever-- 500 people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they were counted over there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "In meantime, [SIGHS] my sister said, they are going-- we are going to be all alone, Shari.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We were in Plaszow together, in Auschwitz together.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And no, we have to be together.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, OK, we are going to try to go closer to count us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What happened?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My sister went to the other side where they were.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said myself, my God-- and they closed up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Here I am alone.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She's over there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What's going to happen?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They don't let me go over there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And nobody can come back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And a few minutes, everybody waiting, few hundred people were this side. 500 people were this side.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, somebody from the back, a girl, a SS, hold on her, and throw her back.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was my sister.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was 501-- and needed 500.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Isn't it God did it?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I believe very firmly this was God.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "God, God helped us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What happened to those 500 girls?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Most of them died.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My, my-- this friend whom was taking care of us, or was supposed to taking care of us, she went-- she lost her mind.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then she died.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And some people-- of her-- one of her sister is still alive.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But she was-- this I don't understand.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If I run by a doctor-- would explain to me-- maybe you can explain to me-- how it happen.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She was about 6 foot 2.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I saw her a few years here in Los Angeles, came to visit a brother.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She's not, not taller than I am.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I couldn't recognize her.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
